INSERT INTO `trk_posts` VALUES ('217', '1', '2016-05-21 02:02:24', '2016-05-21 02:02:24', 'Methylsilanol Mannuronate is an organic derivative of seaweed that binds moisture in the epidermis therefore firming and strengthening the skin.The sea algae extra found in Methylsilanol Mannuronate has long-lasting moisturizing properties that help combat the deterioration of collagen and elastin fibers, giving it skin firming properties; it is also known to fight free radicals.', 'Methylsilanol Mannuronate', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'methylsilanol-mannuronate-2', '', '', '2016-05-21 02:02:24', '2016-05-21 02:02:24', '', '0', 'http://namvang.vn/?post_type=recipe&#038;p=217', '0', 'recipe', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `trk_posts` VALUES ('218', '1', '2016-05-21 02:02:58', '2016-05-21 02:02:58', 'Sufficient scientific studies have been done in Europe and the U.S to know that this oil has the unique ability to promote the formation of new skin tissue and that it possesses anti-inflammatory, anti-neuralgic, antibiotic and antioxidant properties. Tamanu Oil uses include Tamanu Oil acne removal, reduction and or prevention of acne scars, age spots and even stretch marks through to alleviating dry, flaky skin and as an essential ingredient in anti wrinkle creams and for anti aging generally.', 'Tamanu Oil (Calophyllum inophyllum seed oil)', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'tamanu-oil-calophyllum-inophyllum-seed-oil', '', '', '2016-05-21 02:02:58', '2016-05-21 02:02:58', '', '0', 'http://namvang.vn/?post_type=recipe&#038;p=218', '0', 'recipe', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `trk_posts` VALUES ('219', '1', '2016-05-21 02:03:31', '2016-05-21 02:03:31', 'Moisture-rich butter obtained from the nuts of the Mangifolia tree in Central Africa, also known as karite butter or African butter. A superb emollient, high in fatty acids and other nutrients, it is an ideal ingredient for skin moisturizers, sun care products and hair conditioners.', 'Shea Butter', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'shea-butter', '', '', '2016-05-21 02:03:31', '2016-05-21 02:03:31', '', '0', 'http://namvang.vn/?post_type=recipe&#038;p=219', '0', 'recipe', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `trk_posts` VALUES ('220', '1', '2016-05-21 02:04:10', '2016-05-21 02:04:10', 'Honey has a long tradition as a cosmetic ingredient. It contains enzymes, amino acids, minerals and enzymes. Its consistency and color is determined by the plants from which it originates and is seen to be not a quality characteristic. Honey has antibacterial properties. In addition, it also has a moisturising effect. In higher concentrations, honey stimulates the blood circulation and produces a soft feeling.', 'Honey', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'honey', '', '', '2016-05-21 02:04:10', '2016-05-21 02:04:10', '', '0', 'http://namvang.vn/?post_type=recipe&#038;p=220', '0', 'recipe', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `trk_posts` VALUES ('221', '1', '2016-05-21 02:04:43', '2016-05-21 02:04:43', 'Garlic contains essential elements including sulfur, copper, vitamin C, selenium, and minerals that are highly beneficial for hair growth. The copper in garlic promotes hair growth, thickens your hair, and intensifies hair color. To treat a deficiency of any of the above mentioned elements you can rely absolutely on wonderful, versatile garlic.', 'IODIZED GARLIC EXTRACT', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'iodized-garlic-extract', '', '', '2016-05-21 02:07:22', '2016-05-21 02:07:22', '', '0', 'http://namvang.vn/?post_type=recipe&#038;p=221', '0', 'recipe', '', '0');
